title: It Feels Good to Be Home feat. Fat & Paid | Ep. 11
itunes:title: It Feels Good to Be Home feat. Fat & Paid | Ep. 11
description:
Karlous & DC Young Fly are back home in Atlanta fresh from L.A., but somebody forgot to tell Chico. The crew is joined by DC's childhood friend Fat & Paid and the old friends roast each other non-stop. Since they're back in the A, they give A-Town history, A-Town do's & don'ts and since it's the end of Black History Month - the crew are making last minute racial draft trades. Listen in. Download, subscribe, leave a comment and tell a friend to tell a friend!
